ZH: 与民同乐是我们中国传统文化的重要组成部分。
EN: Enjoying happiness with the people is an important aspect of our traditional Chinese culture.

ZH: 我们应该与民同乐，共同分享生活中的快乐和烦恼。
EN: We should enjoy happiness with the people, sharing both joys and sorrows in life.

